__pycache__/     ← compiled Python bytecode, auto-generated
*.py[cod]        ← .pyc, .pyo, .pyd compiled files
.venv/ venv/     ← virtual environment folders (huge, don't upload)
dist/ build/     ← package build folders

node_modules/    ← installed npm packages (huge, don't upload)
npm-debug.log    ← error logs

backups/         ← folders your scripts CREATE (don't upload outputs)
log_archives/
*.tar.gz         ← backup zip files your scripts generate
cleaned_*.csv    ← cleaned CSV outputs your scripts generate
report.txt       ← profiler reports your scripts generate

.DS_Store        ← Mac hidden folder metadata file
Thumbs.db        ← Windows thumbnail cache file
